            "tab_1_heading": "Description",
            "tab_1_content_type": "text",
            "tab_1_text": "<p>Build strength, increase muscle output, and train harder with 5g of pure, micronized creatine monohydrate that helps your body produce fast, reliable energy. Creatine’s natural brain benefits also support sharper focus and mental clarity, so your mind stays as strong as your muscles.</p>",
