            "tab_1_caption_5": "",
            "tab_1_caption_6": "",
            "tab_2_enabled": true,
            "tab_2_heading": "Nutrition",
            "tab_2_content_type": "text",
            "tab_2_text": "<h2>Supplement Facts</h2><p>Serving Size: 1 Scoop (5g)</p><p>Servings Per Container:</p><p>AMOUNT PER SERVING%DV Creatine Monohydrate5 g**** Daily Value (DV) not established</p><p><br/></p><p><strong>OTHER INGREDIENTS: </strong>None</p><h4>WARNING</h4><p>IF YOU HAVE ANY HEALTH CONDITIONS, ARE PREGNANT, BREAST FEEDING OR TAKING MEDICATION, ASK A PHYSICIAN BEFORE USE. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF SMALL CHILDREN.</p><p>ΔTHESE STATEMENTS HAVE NOT BEEN EVALUATED BY THE FOOD AND DRUG ADMINISTRATION. THIS PRODUCT IS NOT INTENDED TO DIAGNOSE, TREAT, CURE, OR PREVENT ANY DISEASE.</p>",
            "tab_2_caption_1": "Vanilla",
            "tab_2_caption_2": "",
            "tab_2_caption_3": "Chocolate",
            "tab_2_caption_4": "",
            "tab_2_caption_5": "",
            "tab_2_caption_6": "",
            "tab_3_enabled": true,
            "tab_3_heading": "Directions",
            "tab_3_content_type": "text",
            "tab_3_text": "<p>Take one serving (1 scoop) mixed with 8-10 fl. oz. of cold water (or other beverage of your choice) before, during or after training. On non-training days, take one serving (1 scoop) in the morning. Easily mixed and stacked with other products.</p>",
