          }
        },
        "template--15510886875181__894e738c-d102-4245-8b24-f42264ccfba5-167805591942128572-1": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_16_2026_10_16_05_PM.png",
            "heading": "Built for strength",
            "text": "<p>Creatine is the most researched performance ingredient there is, and for good reason. By replenishing your body's ATP, the cellular fuel behind every explosive movement, it helps you push harder, lift heavier, and go longer right when it counts. More power per rep, more reps per set, more progress over time.</p>"
          }
        },
        "row_AhH43k": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_16_2026_10_12_36_PM.png",
            "heading": "More muscle, earned",
            "text": "<p>Every hard session is a chance to grow, and creatine helps you make the most of it. It draws water and nutrients into the muscle and supports the work of building lean mass, so the training you put in actually shows up. Real gains from real ingredients, no shortcuts.</p>"
          }
        },
        "template--15510886875181__894e738c-d102-4245-8b24-f42264ccfba5-167805591942128572-2": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/feature-build-muscle_d869b81d-661b-4e86-bac5-e47261623330.jpg",
            "heading": "Recover and repeat",
            "text": "<p>Get back in the game faster. Creatine helps repair muscle micro-tears and restore glycogen stores between workouts, so you recover quicker, feel less beat up, and stay consistent week after week. Because the best program is the one you can keep showing up for.</p>"
          }
        },
        "4959ee0d-d1fe-4639-92fc-81e688e40b63": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_16_2026_10_19_25_PM.png",
            "heading": "Fuel for your mind",
            "text": "<p>Your brain runs on the same energy system your muscles do. By supporting ATP production in brain cells, creatine helps fuel mental performance and focus, especially when you're tired or training hard. Strength for your body, support for your mind.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
